# direnv hook for the nix flake. If you have `direnv` installed and
# `nix-direnv` configured, entering this directory automatically drops you
# into the flake's devShell (and any change to flake.nix re-evaluates).
#
# First-time setup:
#   1. Install direnv: https://direnv.net/docs/installation.html
#   2. (Recommended) Install nix-direnv for faster, cached flake loads:
#      https://github.com/nix-community/nix-direnv
#   3. Allow this file:  direnv allow
#
# Without direnv, just run `nix develop` from the repo root manually.

use flake
